reagan vetoed an earlier pentagon budget bill because he 
objected to its reductions in his request for star wars 
antimissile spending and democraticadded arms control policy 
restrictions he opposes 
when he vetoed the bill wednesday reagan indicated he might be 
able to accept the appropriations measure which contains the same 
cuts in spending for the strategic defense initiative as star wars 
is formally known but none of the arms control limitations 
however those restrictions could be added as the senate tries 
